maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Here we are.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Nous y voilà.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: This cave will directly lead to Vermillion Wasteland.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Cette cave va nous mener tout droit vers \v[area.arid.name].

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: It really is here...
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: J'y crois pas...

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: A whole new area of the playground!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Une toute nouvelle région du jeu !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: This is exciting!!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: C'est si réjouissant !!

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Now this is the last chance for everyone to prepare!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Maintenant c'est votre dernière chance à vous tous pour vous préparer !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Once we go through here, there is no turning back!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Une fois qu'on y entrera, on ne pourra plus revenir en arrière !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: We will have to act quickly to catch Sidwell by surprise!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Il faudra qu'on agisse vite pour prendre Sidwell par surprise !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Lea, please enter the cave once you feel ready to start.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Lea, entre dans la cave dès que tu te sens prête.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: This is your last chance to prepare. When ready, enter the cave in \c[3]Sapphire Ridge - Hidden Entrance\c[0]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Dernière chance pour se préparer. Si vous êtes prêt, entrez dans la cave à l'\c[3]Entrée Cachée de la \v[area.forest.name]\c[0]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: This is it, Lea.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: C'est l'entrée, Lea.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: If we go through that tunnel, we will reach \c[3]Vermillion Wasteland\c[0].
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Si on entre dans ce tunnel, on atteindra \c[3]\v[area.arid.name]\c[0].

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Lukas...\. the Evotar of him...\. he is hopefully still over there.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Lukas...\. son Évotar...\. avec un peu de chance, il est toujours là-bas.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: If we act fast enough, we might still be able to rescue him.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Si on agit assez rapidement, on aura peut-être encore une chance de le sauver.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Lea!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Lea !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Lea, please stop.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Lea, stop.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Running in there alone and unprepared is destined to fail.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Y aller toute seule sans se préparer est voué à l'échec.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Do not worry.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Ne t'inquiète pas.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I am pretty positive that we will find a way to reach the Evotar server.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je suis assez certain qu'on trouvera le moyen d'atteindre le serveur des Évotars.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: To be honest... I am more concerned about what comes afterwards.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Pour être honnête... je m'inquiète plus de ce qui se passera après.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Why?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Pourquoi ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Assuming that we reach the server and manage to make a backup of all the Evotars.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: En supposant qu'on réussisse à atteindre le serveur et qu'on fasse une copie de sauvegarde de tous les Évotars.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: We still need a proper environment to run them.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Il nous faudra encore un véritable environnement pour les faire fonctionner.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: A new place for Evotars.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Un nouvel endroit pour les Évotars.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: And one way or another, we need Instatainment's permission for that.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Et d'une manière où d'une autre, il nous faudra l'autorisation d'Instatainment pour ça.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I am not entirely sure how to tackle this issue, yet.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je ne sais pas encore, comment il faut traiter ce problème, pour l'instant.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Even for an employee like me it is difficult to reach the right people to talk to about this.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Même pour un employé comme moi, ce sera difficile d'avoir les bonnes personnes en face pour parler de ça.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Well, that certainly dampened the mood, I am sorry.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Bon, ça n'a certainement pas remonté le moral, désolé.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: There really is no point in worrying about this now.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Ça ne sert à rien de s'inquiéter de ça pour l'instant.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: We just have to try our best and see what happens.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Il faut juste qu'on essaye de notre mieux et qu'on regarde comment ça se passe.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Waiting it out simply is not an option.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: On ne peut pas se permettre de simplement attendre.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Let us head back.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Bon, revenons sur nos pas.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Are you ready to storm Vermillion Wasteland?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Tu es prête à envahir \v[area.arid.name] ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Good. Everyone get ready!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Bien. Préparez-vous tout le monde !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: The time has come!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Le temps est venu !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Let us proceed through the cave and assemble right before the exit!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Allons tous dans la cave et rassemblons-nous juste avant la sortie !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I will give you further instructions on what to do when we are there!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je vous donnerai plus d'instructions quand on y sera !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Alrighty!\. Let's go everyone!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: C'est bon !\. Allons-y tout le monde !

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [shakes head]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Alright. Make sure you are well prepared.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Bien. Assure-toi d'être bien préparée.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [yes]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [oui]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [no]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [non]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: They closed it off for good, huh?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Ils l'ont fermé pour de bon, hein ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: When I saw the stars up there, I suddenly remembered a lot of things.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Quand j'ai vu les étoiles là-bas, soudainement, je me suis souvenu d'un tas de choses.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: And \c[3]Vermillion Wasteland\c[0]...\. was one of them.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Et \c[3]\v[area.arid.name]\c[0]...\. en faisait partie.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: ...Why?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: ... Pourquoi ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Because...\. I was there.\. Many times.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Parce que...\. J'ai été là-bas.\. Plusieurs fois.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: And I helped...\. to make it all happen.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Et j'ai aidé...\. à faire fonctionner tout ça.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: My task was...\. to keep watching you.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Mon devoir était...\. de te surveiller.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Why?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Pourquoi ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I...\. don't know.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: J...\. Je sais pas.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: A lot of it is still fuzzy.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Tout est encore trop confus.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I just remember, that I didn't want you to find out.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je me souvenais juste, que je ne voulais pas que tu le saches.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I suppose that's what I was...
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je suppose que c'est ce que j'étais.
Un \c[3]espion\c[0]...

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Deceiving you...\. all this time.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: De te duper...\. pendant tout ce temps.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Why?!
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Pourquoi ?!
Je...

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I don't know what else to say...
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je ne sais pas quoi dire d'autre...

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Let's take things slowly, C'tron.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Prenons les choses calmement, C'tron.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Huh?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Hein ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: It's good that your memory seems to be returning so quickly.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: C'est bien que ta mémoire ait l'air de revenir aussi rapidement.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: Do you remember enough to understand the situation you are in right now?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Est-ce que tu te souviens d'assez de choses pour comprendre la situation dans lequel tu es en ce moment ?

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I think I do.
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je pense que oui.

maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.orig: I'm an Evotar, right?
maps/forest/path-10-hidden.json/entities.text: Je suis un Évotar, pas vrai ?

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/768/se.orig: This place of training shall only be open to those deemed worthy.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/768/se.text: Ce lieu d'entrainement ne s'ouvrira qu'à ceux qui en sont dignes.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/769/se.orig: Lea? The \c[3]hidden entrance\c[0] should be around here, but please make sure nobody is in your party before we have a look at it.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/769/se.text: Lea ? l'\c[3]Entrée secrète\c[0] devrait être par ici, mais assure-toi que personne ne soit dans ton groupe avant qu'on y jette un coup d'œil.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/769/se.orig: Okay, we are at the \c[3]Old Dojo\c[0] now. The hidden entrance should be somewhere towards the \c[3]east\c[0].
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/769/se.text: OK, on est à l'\c[3]Ancien Dojo\c[0] maintenant. L'entrée secrète devrait être à l'\c[3]est\c[0].

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/772/se.text: Je crois que je l'ai trouvée !

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/772/se.orig: It is right here, that wall to the east. Let me see if I can open it...
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/772/se.text: Elle est juste là, ce mur à l'est. Voyons voir si je peux l'ouvrir...

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/772/se.orig: Let us see what we find in there.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/772/se.text: Regardons un peu ce qu'on peut y trouver.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/774/se.orig: Could you go to the \c[3]First Scholar HQ\c[0]?
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/774/se.text: Est-ce que tu peux faire un saut vers le \c[3]QG des Premiers Érudits\c[0] ?

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/774/se.orig: I would like to try something out.
Sergey wants you to go to the \c[3]First Scholar HQ\c[0] to test something.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/774/se.text: Sergey veut que vous ailliez au \c[3]QG des Premiers Érudits\c[0] pour tester quelque chose.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/776/se.orig: We've all gathered and are ready!
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/776/se.text: On est tous réunis et on est prêts !

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/776/se.orig: Good!\. Then let us reveal the secret entrance.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/776/se.text: Bien !\. Alors laissez nous vous révéler l'entrée secrète.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/783/se.orig: Lea, we must not enter this area with anyone else.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/783/se.text: Lea, il ne faut pas qu'on entre là-bas avec quiconque.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/783/se.orig: Make sure to disband your party before you proceed.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/783/se.text: Fait en sorte de dissoudre ton groupe avant de continuer.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/784/se.text: Je suis juste à côté de toi...

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/784/se.orig: Whoops!\. Sorry, you're just easy to miss in the bamboo.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/784/se.text: Oups.\. Désolé, c'est trop facile de te rater au milieu des bambous.

maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/784/se.orig: Yes, yes.\. Green hair, I get it.
maps/forest/path-10.json/entities/784/se.text: Oui, oui.\. Cheveux verts, j'ai compris.

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.orig: Sacrebleu, that was one hell of a parkour to get here!
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.text: Sacrebleu, ça en fait du parkour à faire pour arriver jusqu'ici !

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.orig: Gosh, that was a lot of jumping. It better be worth it!
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.text: Pfiou, ça en faisait, des sauts. Ça a intérêt à en valoir la peine !

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.orig: That was quite the challenging parkour, indeed! Today, we honed our Spheromancer skills even further!
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.text: C'était véritablement un parkour difficile, effectivement ! Aujourd'hui encore, nous avons amélioré nos talents de Spheromanceur !

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.orig: How did we even get up here?\. I totally lost track.
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/678/se.text: Comment on a fait pour monter ici ?\. J'ai perdu le fil.

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.orig: Dear Seekers, thank you very much for your ongoing support.
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.text: Chers \v[lore.title.seeker]s, merci pour votre soutien continu.

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.orig: It is thanks to all of you that operation \c[3]Track Walker\c[0] has come this far.
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.text: C'est grâce à vous tous que l'opération \c[3]Retraçage\c[0] a pu aller aussi loin.
La grosse M.a.j, c'est cette année ?

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.orig: We are currently hard at work to make this Temple accessible in the near future.
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.text: Nous mettons tout en œuvre pour rendre ce temple accessible dans le futur proche.
Je veux ma fin là maintenant !!

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.orig: You think anyone from Instatainment is listening to us?
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.text: Tu penses que quelqu'un d'Instatainment nous écoute ?

maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.orig: It's always the same with these game productions.
maps/forest/path-12.json/entities/693/se.text: C'est toujours la même chose avec ces producteurs de jeux.
